node.text:
✨Don’t be fooled by appearance! This little girl with the blue biquíni (me), didn’t forget where she is from.....regardless of everything I have achieved professionally and as a model. The values that my strong yet gentle mom/grandma and my beautiful country Brazil thought me are the virtues that brought me to the top of my career.
I am still that same girl with same essence. I am grateful.....
That being said.... ALWAYS BE TRUTHFUL  AND NEVER DISCONNECT FROM YOUR ROOTS ✨ 🙏🏼
